<H1>  HIERARCHICAL EXACT REACTION LEAPING</H1> 
<HR>
<TABLE WIDTH="90%">
<TR>
<TD WIDTH="30%">
<IMG ALIGN="right" SRC="http://www.uci.edu/graphic_identity/images/downloads/uci_seal_solid.jpg" WIDTH="226">
